## ðŸ“¦ Setup Instructions

1. Clone this repository.
2. Open the `index.html` file in your browser.
3. Enter a city name and click **Submit**.

## ðŸ”‘ API Key

This project uses OpenWeatherMap. Get your free API key from:
https://openweathermap.org/api

Replace the `appid` in the JavaScript file with your own key.

```javascript
let url = `https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q=${cityName}&appid=YOUR_API_KEY&units=metric`;
```
